<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Elit Developers Lab - Projeler</title>
    <style>
        /* Genel Tasarım */
        body {
            background-color: #0f0f0f;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #00ffcc;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.5);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* Kart Konteyneri */
        .container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            max-width: 1000px;
        }

        /* Oyun Kutuları */
        .card {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 250px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: #00ffcc;
        }

        .card h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #aaa;
        }

        /* İnstall Butonu */
        .btn-install {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #00ffcc;
            color: #0f0f0f;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-install:hover {
            background-color: #00cca3;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Elit Developers Lab</h1>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Poxel.io</h2>
            <p>Poxel.io için geliştirilmiş özel script ve modifikasyonlar.</p>
            <a href="BURAYA_INDIRME_LINKINI_YAZ" class="btn-install">Install</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>VSC</h2>
            <p>Visual Studio Code projeleri ve geliştirici araçları.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>IO Oyunları</h2>
            <p>Favori .io oyunları için hazırlanan projeler ve dashboardlar.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        © 2026 ElitHan - Tüm Hakları Saklıdır.
    </footer>

</body>
</html><img src="img/logo.ico" alt="Logo" class="site-logo">